claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: CONSORT flow diagram illustrating Year 1 (2018–2019) enrollment and randomization of 723 participants into four vaccine arms (ccIIV4, RIV, Fluzone IIV4, Fluarix IIV4) with age breakdowns and visit completion, followed by Year 2 re-enrollment and re-randomization of participants into various vaccine sequences. does not support the claim because the image only depicts participant enrollment, randomization, and visit completion; it provides no data on antigenic matching to WHO- or FDA-selected influenza strains.
